Alberta Sackey (amuru na Nọvemba 6, 1972) bu onye Ghana onye agbagoro agbagoro agbagoro agbagoro agbagoro agbagoro dika onye n'iru
Ọ gbara maka Ghana na 1999 FIFA Women's World Cup na 2003 FIFA World Cup ụmụ nwanyị
Goolu ya megide Australia na 2003 World Cup ka ahọpụtara na FIFA.com maka ihe mgbaru ọsọ kachasị ukwuu na akụkọ ntolite iko mba ụwa ụmụ nwanyị
Ọ bụ onye egwuregwu bọọlụ ụmụ nwanyị Afrịka nke afọ 2002.
